Date:  0/0/1988
Source:  Dictionary of Kiwi Slang, A
Author:  McGILL
Vol / Page:  48
Edition:
Quote:  GAFU God Almighty fuck-up; the WWII NZ Second Expeditionary Force variation of the RAF's SNAFU (Situation Normal All Fucked Up), usually a reference to decisions that landed fighting men in impossible  situations. [Jim Henderson]
Notes:  WWII
